Package ohos.agp.text.richstyles

Class RichStyle.Capability

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.text.richstyles.RichStyle.Capability
  • Enclosing class:
    RichStyle

    public static class RichStyle.Capability
extends Object
    Implements capabilities of rich styles. The capabilities affect the character appearance and paragraph presentation.
    Since:
    7
